comments: Thompson (BOS) makes contact with Williams' (LAC) body during his driving shot attempt.
Thompson (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Williams' (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Ibaka (LAC) legally contests Walker's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Williams (BOS) and Morris Sr. (LAC) simultaneously make contact with the ball during the rebound and as Williams disengages with Morris, he makes marginal contact with Morris' arm.
Leonard (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Walker's (BOS) path and does not deliver any contact.
Ibaka (LAC) could be deemed to be in the lane for less than three seconds when the shot is imminent.
Walker (BOS) legally contests Batum's (LAC) jump shot attempt.
Tatum (BOS) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Batum's (LAC) path and does not deliver any contact.
Batum (LAC) maintains a legal defensive position as he defends Tatum (BOS) on-ball.
Ibaka (LAC) makes marginal contact with Thompson (BOS) as they both attempt to make a play on the loose ball.
BOS fails to attempt a shot within 24 seconds. A 24 second violation is correctly assessed and possession is awarded to LAC.
Walker (BOS) makes marginal contact with Leonard (LAC) at the start of the drive.
Williams (BOS) legally contests Williams' (LAC) jump shot attempt.
As Leonard (LAC) releases his dribble to cross the ball over away from Tatum (BOS), Tatum makes slight contact with Leonard's off arm.

At the start of the drive, Ojeleye (BOS) slides a hand across Leonard's (LAC) front without affecting his SQBR then immediately corrects himself to a legal defensive position.
Ojeleye (BOS) legally contests Leonard's (LAC) jump shot attempt. After Leonard returns to the floor, Ojeleye makes incidental foot to foot contact with Leonard.
